-
It's an honor to participate and work with the whole team of professionals!
-
we invite you to travel to our country Dominican Republic by the way! 🔎Research🏖️
-
The Painting includes the national flower of Dominican Republic, the palm trees in the pattern that also represents us, the 3 colors of our flag in the face that are the colors of the French one, and more!❤️
